:<!--Trigger PerformanceE 502065101: Config/Level/NPCDialogue/P10202/NPCAct/Act502065101.json-->
:'''Little Tian:''' Welcome! All our medicines are licensed by the Alchemy Commission and are of the best quality. Please, take your time.
:'''Little Tian:''' Greetings, customer. What do you need?
:<!--Ends the current performance-->
:<!--Custom String Trigger: Talk_502065101-->
