:{{DIcon|Shop}} What have you got for sale here, then?
;(If {{Mission|Back in Business (IV)|showChapter=0}} has been completed)
:{{DIcon|Talk}} Has business been going well lately?
::<!--Trigger PerformanceE 502065201: Config/Level/NPCDialogue/P10202/NPCAct/Act502065201.json-->
::'''Little Tian:''' It's going pretty well. Although the Outworlder tourists are here to travel, they contribute a lot to my medicine sales.
::'''Little Tian:''' The pills I make are known for being easy to consume and store. Some customers ask me to recommend them some supplements after seeing my flawless skin... Well, my skin is in good condition just because I'm in a good space mentally.
::<!--Ends the current performance-->
::<!--Custom String Trigger: Talk_502065201-->
;(If {{Mission|Back in Business (IV)|showChapter=0}} has been completed)
:{{DIcon|Exit}} I don't need anything for now.
::'''Little Tian:''' Thank you for your patronage. See you next time!
::<!--Ends the current performance-->
